Yes sound can be a carrier as well as the silence. People have recorded evp using a variety of methods and tools and conditions. I&#39;ve even had an instance that chainsaw noise was being used and I was able to record some of the speech.
Musical instruments such as guitar and piano tones have also yeilded some results. Ive posted some in the files section here of a few methods and alot on esnips. Links are to the left. 

Misty

